<div id="president">
	<blockquote><p>"Alpha Kappa Psi is the apex of leadership and professionalism in the university setting, as well as a community of like-minded individuals. It boasts a large and internationally-recognized network of professional connections and famous alumni, and we are proud to call ourselves the world's oldest and premier co-ed professional business fraternity. We are a diverse and highly-skilled group of young professionals, and our programming caters to a variety of student interests, from coding to entrepreneurship. We welcome all majors, and offer a wealth of opportunities for professional development and personal growth."</p></blockquote>
